        "TileImage": "$($repository 92532bb0-0f92-4bbe-847f-4c248729cb14).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47 and welocme to Chongqing&apos;s Local Noodle Place.\r\rOur client, Mr Pritchard, wants you to kill these 5 restaurant cooks becouse they secretly poison the food that they are serving to the local people.\r\rThey are planning to poison Mr.  Pritchard. Eliminate them before \rMr Pritchard gets poisoned.\r\rEliminate them with any method and any disguise and Be safe.\r\rGood luck 47.                                       -Diana Burnwood",
